{"_id":"89fBZYwbOuiAb5eD","name":"The Laborer","permission":{"default":0,"6CCGnEQyToQj7t5R":3},"type":"species","data":{"description":"<p><strong>Starting Experience:</strong> 100</p>\n<p><strong>Tough as Nails:</strong> Once per session, your character may spend a Story Point as an out-of-turn incidental immediately after suffering a Critical Injury and determining the result. If they do so, they count the result rolled as &ldquo;01.&rdquo;</p>\n<h2>Alternative</h2><p><b>Ferocious Strike:</b> Once per session, your character may spend <i>a Story Point</i> as an incidental after dealing a Critical Injury and rolling the result. If she does so, she adds 5 × his Brawn to the result rolled before determining the Critical Injury and its effect.</p>","attributes":{"Brawn":{"value":3,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Brawn"},"Agility":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Agility"},"Intellect":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Intellect"},"Cunning":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Cunning"},"Willpower":{"value":1,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Willpower"},"Presence":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Presence"},"Wounds":{"value":12,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Wounds"},"Strain":{"value":8,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Strain"},"attr1609406036195":{"modtype":"Skill Rank","value":1,"mod":"Athletics"}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"_id":"8FfIfWxIw3HkqZdZ","name":"The Intellectual","permission":{"default":0,"6CCGnEQyToQj7t5R":3},"type":"species","data":{"description":"<p><strong>Starting Experience:</strong> 100</p>\n<p><strong>Starting Skills: </strong>An intellectual starts with one rank in Knowledge during character creation. They obtain this rank before spending experience points, and may not increase Knowledge above rank 2 during character creation.</p>\n<p><strong>Brilliant!:</strong> Once per session, your character may spend a Story Point as an incidental. If they do so, during the next check they make during that turn, you count their ranks in the skill being used as equal to their Intellect.</p>\n<h2>Alternative</h2><p><b>Eureka!</b> Once per session, your character may spend <i>a Story Point</i> to make <i>a Knowledge check</i>. Double the [SU] generated by the dice before cancelling results.</p>","attributes":{"Brawn":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Brawn"},"Agility":{"value":1,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Agility"},"Intellect":{"value":3,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Intellect"},"Cunning":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Cunning"},"Willpower":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Willpower"},"Presence":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Presence"},"Wounds":{"value":8,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Wounds"},"Strain":{"value":12,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Strain"}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[]}
{"name":"Average Human","permission":{"default":0,"6CCGnEQyToQj7t5R":3},"type":"species","data":{"description":"<p><strong>Starting Experience:</strong> 110</p>\n<p><strong>Starting Skills:</strong> A natural starts with one rank in each of two different non-career skills at character creation. They obtain this rank before spending experience points, and these skills may not be increased higher than rank 2 during character creation.</p>\n<p><strong>Ready for Anything:</strong> Once per session as an out-of-turn incidental, you may move one Story Point from the Game Master&rsquo;s pool to the players&rsquo; pool.</p>\n<h2>Alternative</h2><p><b>Intuitive Solution:</b></p> Once per session when making a check for which you character has no skill ranks, he may spend <i>a Story Point</i> to use another characteristic in place of the skill’s ranks. The second characteristic should affect how the check’s resolution is described.","attributes":{"Brawn":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Brawn"},"Agility":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Agility"},"Intellect":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Intellect"},"Cunning":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Cunning"},"Willpower":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Willpower"},"Presence":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Presence"},"Wounds":{"value":10,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Wounds"},"Strain":{"value":10,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Strain"}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"bgUCeV1undEQvrmI"}
{"name":"The Aristocrat","permission":{"default":0,"6CCGnEQyToQj7t5R":3},"type":"species","data":{"description":"<p><strong>Starting Experience:</strong> 100</p>\n<p><strong>Forceful Personality:</strong> Once per session, your character may spend a Story Point as an incidental. If they do so, during the next skill check they make during that turn, your character doubles the strain they inflict or the strain they heal (you choose before making the check).</p>\n<h2>Alternative</h2><p><b>Practiced Etiquette:</b> Once per session after a foe makes an opposed social check against your character, you may spend <i>a Story Point</i> as an out-of-turn incidental to remove all [AD] generated by that foe’s check before any symbols are cancelled.</p>","attributes":{"Brawn":{"value":1,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Brawn"},"Agility":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Agility"},"Intellect":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Intellect"},"Cunning":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Cunning"},"Willpower":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Willpower"},"Presence":{"value":3,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Presence"},"Wounds":{"value":10,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Wounds"},"Strain":{"value":10,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Strain"},"attr1609406451521":{"modtype":"Skill Rank","value":1,"mod":"Cool"}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"clDkfKd870NnIDks"}
